description: Removes a custom vocabulary from the specified locale in the specified bot.

parameters.name: botId
parameters.description: The unique identifier of the bot to remove the custom vocabulary from.

parameters.name: botVersion
parameters.description: The version of the bot to remove the custom vocabulary from.

parameters.name: localeId
parameters.description: The locale identifier for the locale that contains the custom vocabulary to remove.
